title: Nathaniel L Cole Discography 2007-2013 (2 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
NATHANIEL L COLE DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 2 releases...

 * 2007 - God Is Waiting
 * 2013 - Listen

When asked what inspired him to do a instrumental Jazz CD, he simply states that instrumental music is his first love and that he started out making music with no words long before he ever thought to write a song with words.

Blessings,
TorrentTracts - October 2013
